Insider Activity


Individual




Ramzi Y. Hermiz



Mr. Ramzi Y. Hermiz is President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Shiloh Industries, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Shiloh Industries, Inc.
Mr. Hermiz was previously employed as Senior Vice President-Vehicle Safety & Protection by Federal-Mogul Corp., Design & Product Engineer by Keldu Technologies Corp., and a Manager-Purchasing & Quality Assurance by Triangle Home Products, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Marquette University and an MBA from DePaul University.



